\ls1\ilvl1\cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\'95	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
1st time: the left foot moves on the left\cb1 \
\ls1\ilvl1\cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\'95	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
2nd time: the right foot joins the left foot\cb1 \
\ls1\ilvl1\cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\'95	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
3d time: the left foot moves again\cb1 \
\ls1\ilvl1\cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\'95	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
4th time: the feet don't move, the body still supported by the left foot\cb1 \
