\ls1\ilvl1\cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\'95	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
5th time: the right foot joins the left foot\cb1 \
\ls1\ilvl1\cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\'95	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
6th time: the left foot marks time (up & down in one time)\cb1 \
\ls1\ilvl1\cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\'95	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
