\cf3 \cb4 It is easy to do this dance within a short time of practice; this allows full beginners to quickly join the line during the {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fest_noz"}}{\fldrslt \cf6 \cb4 festo\'f9 noz}}.\cf3 \cb1 \
